Template: php5-xapian/modifyphpini
Type: boolean
Default: true
_Description: Do you want php.ini to be configured to load Xapian?
 This package can automatically modify the PHP5 ini file to add the necessary
 entry to always load Xapian into PHP.  Alternatively any PHP script which uses
 Xapian can load it explicitly with 'dl("xapian.so");'.
